Version (0.92)

	- "Image Directory" variable added. This makes it easier to use 
	  the same game data with different graphics files. For instance, 
	  if you have a high and a low resolution version of the same 
	  game, you only have to change this entry to point to another 
	  directory, and the rest of the game data remains intact.

	- Inventory display adjusted to now display an "(eqipped)" tag on 
	  the end of all listed equipped items

	- If an obstruction was marked visible but didn't have a graphic,
	  it's name would not get printed to the output area. This has
	  been fixed.

	- CogEngine updated to skip introduction when started with a
	  current room number greater than one (will be useful when saving
	  and loading games becomes available)
